<item>
            <title>[SPARK-20023] Can not see table comment when describe formatted table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-20023</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Spark 2.x implements create table by itself.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/7d2ed8cc030f3d84fea47fded072c320c3d87ca7&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/7d2ed8cc030f3d84fea47fded072c320c3d87ca7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
But in the implement mentioned above, it remove table comment from properties, so user can not see table comment through run &quot;describe formatted table&quot;. Similarly, when user alters table comment, he still can not see the change of table comment through run &quot;describe formatted table&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
I wonder why we removed table comments, is this a bug?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
